                        '判斷當“下一頁”按鈕為網頁的超鏈接<a>元素，且其屬性不爲 .target="_self" 值（不在當前窗口打開新連接）時，先修改 .target 屬性為 "_self" 值（在當前窗口打開新連接），然後再點擊“下一頁”鏈接；函數 LCase() 表示將英文字母字符串大寫轉小寫
                        If (Browser_Object.document.getElementsByTagName(Public_First_level_page_next_button_tag_name)(Public_First_level_page_next_button_position_index).NodeType = 1) And (LCase(Browser_Object.document.getElementsByTagName(Public_First_level_page_next_button_tag_name)(Public_First_level_page_next_button_position_index).nodeName) = "a") And (Browser_Object.document.getElementsByTagName(Public_First_level_page_next_button_tag_name)(Public_First_level_page_next_button_position_index).target <> "_self") Then
