                ElseIf (Start_page_number < Current_page_number) And (First_level_page_back_button_xpath <> "") And (Public_First_level_page_back_button_tag_name <> "") And (Public_First_level_page_back_button_position_index >= 0) Then
                '判斷網頁中是否包含有“下一頁”按鈕，以及傳入的起始頁碼值是否大於當前頁碼號

